OL,3,CHealth watchdog 'not fit for purpose'
OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,FGood Morning Britain's Richard
OL,7,FGaisford reports on the findings
OL,9,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,10,Fsaid that England's health and social
OL,11,Fcare watchdog is "not fit for purpose"
OL,12,Fas he pledged immediate action to
OL,13,Frestore public confidence.
OL,15,FHis comments come after an independent
OL,16,Freview into the Care Quality
OL,17,FCommission (CQC), a body that monitors
OL,18,Fall health and adult social care
OL,19,Fproviders to ensure standards and
OL,20,Fsafety.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
