OL,3,CHealth watchdog 'not fit for purpose'
OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,FThe review found that some
OL,7,Forganisations had not been re-
OL,8,Finspected in several years, with the
OL,9,Foldest rating for an NHS hospital
OL,10,Fdating from more than 10 years ago,
OL,11,Fwhile the oldest for a social care
OL,12,Fprovider was from 2015.
OL,14,FStreeting said that ratings of
OL,15,Fhealthcare providers on the CQC
OL,16,Fwebsite should be taken 'with a pinch
OL,17,Fof salt' and commission has been asked
OL,18,Fto 'urgently qualify' ratings
