OL,3,CHealth watchdog 'not fit for purpose'
OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,FOf the locations the CQC has the power
OL,7,Fto inspect, it is estimated about one
OL,8,Fin five health organisations have
OL,9,Fnever been inspected.
OL,11,FIt was also found that there was a
OL,12,Flack of experience among some staff,
OL,13,Fincluding examples of inspectors
OL,14,Fvisiting hospitals.
OL,16,FSome had said they had never been in a
OL,17,Fhospital prior to conducting an
OL,18,Fassessment and one inspector of a care
OL,19,Fhome stated they had never met someone
OL,20,Fwith dementia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
