OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,FThe report found inspection numbers
OL,7,Fwere still well below pre-Covid level.
OL,9,FIt also found a lack of consistency in
OL,10,Fthe watchdog's assessments and issues
OL,11,Fwith its IT system.
OL,13,FMr Streeting said: "When I joined the
OL,14,Fdepartment, it was already clear that
OL,15,Fthe NHS was broken and the social care
OL,16,Fsystem in crisis.
