OL,6,FWhen asked if there was a fix that did
OL,7,Fnot involve spending more money, Mr
OL,8,FStreeting said: "I don't think money
OL,9,Fis the issue here. I think it's
OL,10,Fculture."
OL,12,FHe said there needs to be a "radical
OL,13,Freform" of the organisation and that
OL,14,Fhe wanted to be clear with potential
OL,15,Fcandidates about the scale of the
OL,16,Fchallenge as he recruits a new
OL,17,Fpermanent chief inspector of hospitals
OL,18,Fto the CQC.
