OL,6,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,7,FCare announced immediate steps to
OL,8,Frestore public confidence in the CQC,
OL,9,Fwhich is appointing Professor Sir Mike
OL,10,FRichards, a former hospital physician
OL,11,Fand its first chief inspector of
OL,12,Fhospitals, to review its assessment
OL,13,Fframework.
OL,15,FTransparency regarding how the
OL,16,Fregulator determines ratings for
OL,17,Fhealth and social care providers will
OL,18,Falso be improved and the government
OL,19,Fwill have increased oversight of the
OL,20,FCQC, the department said.
