OL,6,F"We are working at pace and in
OL,7,Fconsultation with our stakeholders to
OL,8,Frebuild that trust and become the
OL,9,Fstrong, credible, and effective
OL,10,Fregulator of health and care services
OL,11,Fthat the public and providers need and
OL,12,Fdeserve."
OL,14,FProgress will be monitored over the
OL,15,Fsummer and the full independent report
OL,16,Fwill be published in autumn, the
OL,17,FDepartment of Health said.
